{"tid":1928821,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"畀個貼士大家 唔好咁戇鳩","createTime":"2020-03-16T15:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T10:01:20.000Z","uid":353330,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d12ad061a39da17934db762819d700ed4a88acbb","tid":1928821,"uid":353330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔明點解有人仲會入牛想反彈  直接一開始求其一隻認沽證熊證擺返幾個星期都賺到嘔喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼士: 而家仲有得跌 等下個星期反彈嘅時候重貨熊證 之後一係等到佢跌到好低先走或者侵侵未死得 疫情有疫苗 嗰陣先再大手牛證<br />\n<br />\n熊市買咩股: 我買舜宇光學熊證126蚊揸到而家<br />\n<br />\n當牛市來臨應該買咩股: 中國鐵塔  因為可以買牛證 仲有係5g最受期待股票  <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再咁戇鳩啦 唔好估乜嘢恆指最底位啦 <br />\n<br />\n買一隻遠熊證 每到得番一百幾日就轉第二隻熊證<br />\n<br />\n牛市相同玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f393efb5edc33972cc6b4e877cbeb0aa89f000cf","tid":1928821,"uid":38540,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"幾時開班教下巴菲特炒股 隻廢老近排輸好多"},{"pid":"e9cb8bc05d87097920437d9400830407a3c1e5f6","tid":1928821,"uid":353330,"like":